snippet.title: Little Witch Nobeta - Forgotten Souls Trailer | PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Search for the truth of a strange castle in this soulslike, spellbinding shooter.

Little Witch Nobeta launches physically and digitally for PlayStation 4 on the 7th of March, 2023.
